    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The terminology about, and associations among, Real-time Transport Protocol (RTP) sources can be complex and somewhat opaque.  This document describes a number of existing and proposed properties and relationships among RTP sources and defines common terminology for discussing protocol entities and their relationships.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
